nd if it proposes a list of installations to be closed, <PERSON> Carlucci </PERSON> will have to accept or reject the entire list. His decision can be blocked only by a vote of both the <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> and <ORGANIZATION> Senate </ORGANIZATION>. Sen. <PERSON> William </PERSON> <PERSON> Roth </PERSON>, R-Del., said, `` In light of our current budgetary deficit, the need to save $ 2 billion a year is clear and obvious. The commission proposal is not in the <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> version of the <ORGANIZATION> Pentagon </ORGANIZATION> budget measure, but that chamber is expected to consider a separate bill which includes the commission. The competing bills that will be approved in the <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> and <ORGANIZATION> Senate </ORGANIZATION> eventually will go to a conference committee to reconcile differences, including the base-closing plan. Both bills authorize $ 299.5 billion in defense spending for the fiscal year beginning Oct. 1.
