estigation is continuing and that he would oppose the suspect's being relased from jail. `` We got a dangerous man here. If he seeks out two hitmen he is determining his resolve to do something,'' <PERSON> Rodriguez </PERSON> said. <PERSON> Natalia </PERSON>, <PERSON> Abell </PERSON>'s home, is 18 miles southwest of <LOCATION> San </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Antonio </LOCATION>.
