<HEAD>Taiwanese Gangster Gets 27 years-to-Life In Political Murder</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto FX5</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By JACK SCHREIBMAN</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
