<HEAD>International Trade Commission Votes For Sanctions</HEAD>
<HEAD>PD Filed</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 The <ORGANIZATION> International </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Trade </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Commission </ORGANIZATION> plans to impose import duties on forklift trucks allegedly `` dumped'' below cost in the <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION> by Japanese manufacturers. In a unanimous ruling sought by <ORGANIZATION> Hyster </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Co. </ORGANIZATION> of <LOCATION> Portland </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Ore. </LOCATION>, the six-member commission said Tuesday that the <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> forklift industry had suffered `` material injury'' because of the Japanese practices. The ruling means the importers of forklift trucks will have to pay cash duties equal to the dumping margin on each Japanese forklift they import. The <ORGANIZATION> Department </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> of </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Commerce </ORGANIZATION> will determine the dumping margins, with several expected to exceed 50 percent. The <ORGANIZATION> Commerce </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Department </ORGANIZATION> ruled last month that Japanese producers had been dumping their forklifts in the <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION>. Japanese manufacturers have not paid any duties since January 1986. In a petition filed in April 1987, <PERSON> Hyster </PERSON> and four labor unions alleged that Japanese producers were using unfair tactics to claim half of the <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> market in small - to medium-capacity internal combustion lift trucks Such trucks comprise 70 percent of the <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> market. List prices range from $ 14,000 to $ 65,000. Hyster, along with the <ORGANIZATION> United </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Shop </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> and </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Service </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Workers </ORGANIZATION>, the <ORGANIZATION> Independent </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Lift </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Truck </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZAT