 been sitting on <LOCATION> Capitol </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Hill </LOCATION> while the Democrats tried in vain to win over two votes for a veto override by reopening the measure and stripping out its restrictions on <LOCATION> Alaska </LOCATION> oil exports.
